      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document is a revision to STD35, RFC1006.  This document describes the mechanism to allow ISO Transport Services to run over TCP over IPv4 or IPv6.  It also defines a number of new features, which are not provided in RFC1006. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
